## 配置文件格式

配置文件使用 TOML 格式：

```toml
[app]
name = "{{ project_slug }}"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "{{ project_description }}"

[env]
environment = "development"  # development, staging, production, testing
debug = false

[log]
level = "INFO"               # DEBUG, INFO, WARNING, ERROR, CRITICAL
format = "json"              # json, text
output = "console"           # console, file, both
dir_name = "logs"
file_name = "app.log"
max_bytes = 10485760         # 10MB
backup_count = 5

[db]
type = "postgresql"          # postgresql, mysql, sqlite
host = "localhost"
port = 5432
username = "postgres"
password = ""
database = "app"
pool_size = 20
max_overflow = 10
pool_timeout = 30
pool_recycle = 3600
```

### 配置优先级

环境变量可覆盖 TOML 配置，CLI 参数优先级最高：

```
CLI 参数 > 环境变量 (RegModel_*) > .env > TOML 文件 > 默认值
```

环境变量示例：

```bash
export RegModel_env_environment=production
export RegModel_db_host=db.example.com
```
